     - c_mktsegment (customer)
   - **Hash Indexes** (4 indexes): Multi-value design for joins
     - l_orderkey (15M unique), o_orderkey (15M), o_custkey (999K), c_custkey (1.5M)
   - OpenMP parallelization on 64 cores
   - Efficient mmap-based column reading
